front.title: Hidden Compartment
front.gametext: Deploy on any R-unit droid. At start of a battle, you may 'react' by deploying one character weapon (at normal use of the Force) from Reserve Deck on a warrior present; reshuffle.
front.lore: Standard astromech internal cargo area measures 20 centimeters by 8 centimeters. Some models have a custom compressed (AI)r launcher for shooting flares.

pulls: One character weapon at start of battle
